526
00:31:49,174 --> 00:31:52,511
Uh, yeah.

527
00:31:52,511 --> 00:31:55,313
I knew he would say that.

528
00:31:57,415 --> 00:31:59,618
Then you're pitching for him.

529
00:32:08,059 --> 00:32:10,462
Is it time?
Yeah. It's time.

530
00:32:11,496 --> 00:32:13,498
Oh.

531
00:32:13,498 --> 00:32:15,634
Uh, thanks.

532
00:32:15,634 --> 00:32:18,637
[crowd cheering, applauding]

