00:33:20,265 --> 00:33:23,268
<i> Gooden staring into Girardi</i>
<i> for the sign.</i>

554
00:33:23,268 --> 00:33:25,437
<i> He winds, kicks, and deals.</i>

555
00:33:25,437 --> 00:33:27,505
<i> Wilson, fly ball</i>
<i> to center field.</i>

