00:33:27,505 --> 00:33:31,509
<i> Going back is Gerald Williams.</i>
<i> He's there and puts it away.</i>

557
00:33:31,509 --> 00:33:35,313
<i> And Gooden is just</i>
<i> six outs away from history.</i>

