575
00:34:36,408 --> 00:34:39,544
<i>So, Gooden alone</i>
<i>with his thoughts.</i>

576
00:34:39,544 --> 00:34:41,913
<i>Trying to win the game.</i>
<i>Trying to pitch a no-hitter.</i>

577
00:34:41,913 --> 00:34:43,615
<i>And the tying run</i>
<i>at the plate,</i>

578
00:34:43,615 --> 00:34:45,717
<i>the dangerous Edgar Martínez.</i>

