00:34:48,753 --> 00:34:51,356
<i>And Gooden deals.</i>
<i>Breaking ball, outside. </i>
[crowd groaning]

581
00:34:51,356 --> 00:34:52,924
<i>He loses Martinez.</i>

582
00:34:52,924 --> 00:34:55,493
<i> And now the worry isn't</i>
<i> only about the no-hitter,</i>

583
00:34:55,493 --> 00:34:56,828
<i> but about the game.</i>

584
00:34:58,630 --> 00:35:01,600
Is Wetteland ready?
Yeah. He's ready.

585
00:35:03,168 --> 00:35:04,869
<i>Two on, one out</i>
<i>in the 9th inning.</i>

586
00:35:04,869 --> 00:35:07,672
<i>Gooden trying to win</i>
<i>the ball game,</i>
<i>leading 2-nothing,</i>

587
00:35:07,672 --> 00:35:10,642
<i>and earn his place</i>
<i>in baseball history.</i>

