00:35:10,642 --> 00:35:13,845
<i>The pitch to Buhner is low.</i>
<i>Gets away from Girardi.</i>

589
00:35:13,845 --> 00:35:17,382
<i>A wild pitch,</i>
<i>and the runners move</i>
<i>to second and third.</i>

590
00:35:17,382 --> 00:35:19,818
<i> And now a base hit</i>
<i> not only breaks his heart</i>

591
00:35:19,818 --> 00:35:21,820
<i> but ties the game.</i>

592
00:35:23,455 --> 00:35:25,190
Wanna talk to him?

593
00:35:25,190 --> 00:35:26,758
You go.

594
00:35:27,826 --> 00:35:29,761
[crowd cheering]

595
00:35:29,761 --> 00:35:31,429
[blows]

596
00:35:32,564 --> 00:35:34,165
[exhales forcefully]

597
00:35:38,970 --> 00:35:42,540
I'm just here
to give you a breather.
Uh-huh.

598
00:35:42,540 --> 00:35:44,576
Joe says the game's yours.

599
00:35:44,576 --> 00:35:47,812
So just try to relax
as best you can, hmm?

600
00:35:47,812 --> 00:35:49,681
Mm.

