00:35:49,681 --> 00:35:51,916
If this guy's
gonna hurt you,

602
00:35:51,916 --> 00:35:53,918
make him hurt you
on your pitch.

603
00:35:53,918 --> 00:35:55,553
All right?
Mm.

604
00:35:55,553 --> 00:35:57,555
All right.
[pats back]

605
00:36:01,993 --> 00:36:04,696
[cheering continues]

606
00:36:07,932 --> 00:36:09,868
It's great.

