00:36:11,569 --> 00:36:12,971
<i>One out to go.</i>

608
00:36:12,971 --> 00:36:15,674
<i>One out in the bottom</i>
<i>of the 9th for Gooden to get.</i>

609
00:36:15,674 --> 00:36:19,444
<i>The left-hand hitting</i>
<i>Paul Sorrento,</i>
<i>and it'll be a one-two pitch,</i>

