00:36:19,444 --> 00:36:21,446
<i>with tying runs</i>
<i>at second and third.</i>

611
00:36:21,446 --> 00:36:23,782
<i>Now Gooden is set.</i>
<i>The pitch.</i>

612
00:36:23,782 --> 00:36:25,950
<i>He pops it up!</i>
