00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:34,592
<i>Jeter makes the catch! </i>
Yeah!

616
00:36:34,592 --> 00:36:36,628
<i>Dwight Gooden pitched</i>
<i>a no-hitter! </i>

617
00:36:36,628 --> 00:36:39,597
