00:36:44,469 --> 00:36:46,471
<i> of his long,</i>
<i> illustrious career.</i>

621
00:36:46,471 --> 00:36:50,542
<i> Remember, this is a guy</i>
<i> who suffered</i>
<i> in the depths of drugs,</i>

622
00:36:50,542 --> 00:36:52,677
<i> and right now,</i>
<i> here in the grass,</i>

623
00:36:52,677 --> 00:36:54,979
<i> he is sitting</i>
<i> on top of the world.</i>

624
00:36:54,979 --> 00:36:57,482
[crowd cheering]

